data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a highly sought-after neighborhood! This charming 3-bedroom residence boasts unparalleled curb appeal, captivating passersby with its meticulously landscaped front yard and inviting facade. Step inside to discover a seamlessly designed open floor concept, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere throughout the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Natural light streams through large windows, accentuating the tasteful finishes and modern aesthetic. The generously sized bedrooms offer comfort and versatility, while the master suite provides a private oasis. As you venture outside, the oversized backyard awaits, providing an expansive and private retreat perfect for entertaining or enjoying tranquil moments. This residence not only offers a comfortable and stylish living space but also the lifestyle you've been searching for in a desirable and established community. Its also a school bus route which makes it perfect for your little ones. Welcome home!
